<section id="about" class="asymmetric-grid" style="padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-md); max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; align-items: center;">
  <div class="asymmetric-item left animate-fade-in delay-300" style="position: relative;">
    <div style="position: absolute; top: -20px; left: -20px; width: 100px; height: 100px; background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2); filter: blur(30px); border-radius: 50%;"></div>
    <img 
      src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iODAwIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSJ0cmFuc3BhcmVudCIvPjwvc3ZnPg==" 
      data-src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" 
      alt="Architecture Geometry" 
      style="width: 100%; border-radius: 2px; position: relative; z-index: 1;" 
    />
  </div>

  <div class="asymmetric-item right animate-fade-in delay-100" style="padding-left: var(--space-lg);">
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-4xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">The <span class="text-accent">Mission.</span></h2>
    <div style="font-size: var(--text-lg); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); color: white;">
      Administrative friction is the enemy of velocity. We eliminate it.
    </div>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">
      Automate Momentum exists to bridge the gap between heavy operational drag and zero-friction execution. By developing specialized AI-driven systems and deploying dynamic agent networks, we allow organizations to radically scale without scaling their headcount.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">
      Our leadership stems from deep experience steering development teams to produce executive-grade intelligence autonomously. From automated contract analysis to outbound amplification, if it can be codified, we will automate it to perfection.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
